data.description: This all-brick home built by “Custom Homes By Jeff” is 3159 sq ft with 4 bedrooms, 3.5 bathrooms with large Bonus RM. Beautiful Hardwood flooring in living room, kitchen, dining room, and breakfast nook and tile in bathrooms/laundry. Stainless steel appliances in kitchen with large walk in pantry. Spacious laundry room with cabinets for storage. Carpet in all bedrooms. Coffered/tray ceilings, and crown molding throughout entire home. 1st floor Master suite features Large walk-in closet, jetted tub, and fully tiled, walk-in shower. 4 bedrooms upstairs with 2 rooms set up as jack and jill. Relax on the beautiful front porch or enjoy the covered grilling back porch with privacy fence. Property sits on (.33 acres) equipped with front and back irrigation system on well maintained sodded yard and landscaping. Home has attached 2-car garage. Outstanding school zone.
